OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 17 JUN
OL,4,CMISCELLANEOUS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1959FThe BBC Cablefilm system is put
OL,7,Fto its first official use when the
OL,8,FQueen and President Eisenhower open the
OL,9,FSt Lawrence seaway in 1959.
OL,10,
OL,11,FThe BBC Engineering Research and
OL,12,FDesigns Departments co-operated in
OL,13,Fdesigning and manufacturing two sets of
OL,14,Fequipment for sending and recording
OL,15,Fshort pieces of 16mm film over a
OL,16,Ftransatlantic music circuit.
OL,17,
OL,18,FOne set was installed in Canada and the
OL,19,Fother at Alexandra Palace.
